name: BacterialSkinCommensals
title: Bacterial Skin Commensals
description: Created for reporting to the National Healthcare Safety Network (NHSN).
purpose: (Clinical Focus: Normal bacterial inhabitants of the skin.),(Data Element Scope: Microorganisms identified from laboratory tests.),(Inclusion Criteria: Members from more than 30 genera and expected to grow),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude known pathogens, 2 so far: Bacillus anthracis and Corynebacterium diphtheriae)
